ions. We show that it is feasible to constrain the UHECN flavor\nratio using the proposed ARA Observatory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Feb 2013 21:03:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 30 Nov 2013 12:44:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-03"}
